# Laporan Update YamiSend

## Arsitektur & Stack
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express + TypeScript + `ws` (WebSocket) + Multer (upload)
- **Frontend Mobile:** Flutter (Android) + `http` + `web_socket_channel` + `mobile_scanner` (QR)
- **CLI:** Built-in di server (readline), bisa kirim file dari laptop
- **Port:** 3000
- **WebSocket:** Port sama (3000), upgrade dari HTTP, path `/` dengan query `?sessionId=xxx`

---

## Fitur & Kemampuan Lengkap

### 1. Host Session (Backend Startup)
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/server.ts`
- Server start â†’ `initHostSession()` bikin satu host session (UUID random)
- Upload folder: `src/uploads/<sessionId>/` (semua client HP & CLI share folder yang sama)
- QR code langsung tampil di terminal saat startup
- CLI langsung aktif (prompt `>`)

### 2. Session Management
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/routes/session.route.ts`
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/sessions/session.store.ts`
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/sessions/host.session.ts`
- **GET `/session/host`** â€” Ambil host session (dipanggil Flutter saat manual connect IP)
- **GET `/session/create`** â€” Buat session baru + QR (untuk SessionScreen)
- **GET `/session/:id/join`** â€” Join session (mendaftarkan IP sebagai client, dipanggil HP)
- **GET `/session/:id/files`** â€” List file di session
- **GET `/session/:id/download/:filename`** â€” Download file dari session
- **POST `/session/:id/upload`** â€” Upload file ke session (broadcast WebSocket)
- Session store in-memory (`Map<string, Session>`)

### 3. Upload (HP â†’ Laptop)
**File:** `yami_send/lib/features/files/file_service.dart` (extension `FileUpload`)
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/routes/session.route.ts` (POST `/session/:id/upload`)
- HP pilih file pake `file_picker`
- Upload via `http.MultipartRequest`
- Server simpan di `src/uploads/<sessionId>/`
- Nama file: `timestamp-originalName` (multer)
- Broadcast WS event `file_uploaded` ke semua client di session yang sama

### 4. Download (Laptop â†’ HP)
**File:** `yami_send/lib/features/files/file_service.dart` (extension `FileDownload`)
**File:** `yami_send/lib/core/download_service.dart`
- HP minta file â†’ `GET /session/:id/download/:filename`
- Response dikirim sebagai bytes
- Disimpan otomatis ke folder sesuai tipe:
  - `jpg/jpeg/png/gif/webp/svg/bmp` â†’ `Pictures/YamiSend/`
  - `mp4/mkv/avi/mov/wmv` â†’ `Movies/YamiSend/`
  - `mp3/wav/aac/ogg/flac` â†’ `Music/YamiSend/`
  - `pdf/doc/docx/xls/xlsx/ppt/pptx/txt/zip/rar` â†’ `Documents/YamiSend/`
  - lainnya â†’ `Download/YamiSend/`
- Base path: `/storage/emulated/0/`

### 5. WebSocket Realtime
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/socket/socket.manager.ts`
**File:** `yami_send/lib/core/socket_service.dart`
- WS server di port 3000 (satu server dengan HTTP)
- Flutter connect: `ws://<ip>:3000?sessionId=xxx`
- Event: `file_uploaded` â€” data: `{ filename, originalName, size }`
- Flutter `SocketService` â†’ `ValueNotifier<int>` â†’ `FileListWidget` auto refresh
- WS auto-connect setelah session established
- WS disconnect saat manual disconnect

### 6. CLI (Laptop)
**File:** `yamisend-server/src/cli/host.cli.ts`
