## Alur Data (Flow)

### Upload HP â†’ Laptop
```
HP pick file
  â†’ POST /session/:id/upload (multipart)
  â†’ Server simpan di src/uploads/<sessionId>/
  â†’ Server broadcast WS "file_uploaded"
  â†’ HP (via WS) & Laptop (via CLI files) lihat file baru
```

### Download Laptop â†’ HP
```
HP tap download icon
  â†’ GET /session/:id/download/:filename
  â†’ Server kirim file bytes
  â†’ DownloadService.saveFile(filename, bytes)
  â†’ Tersimpan di /storage/emulated/0/<type>/YamiSend/<filename>
  â†’ Snackbar kasih tau path lengkap
  â†’ Icon berubah jadi check hijau
```

### Send CLI â†’ HP
```
Laptop: send /path/to/video.mp4
  â†’ Copy file ke src/uploads/<sessionId>/video.mp4
  â†’ emitFileUploaded() via WS
  â†’ HP auto refresh (WS event â†’ ValueNotifier â†’ load())
  â†’ HP lihat file baru + bisa download
```

